            . I am an officer. On the 12th of March, about nine o'clock, I saw the prisoner turn the corner of Grafton-street, with this coat under his arm; I asked where he got it - he said he brought it from home; I opened it, and found a shop-ticket on it, with Wadmore's address at the back - I secured him.</p>
